## Constraints

### Use

- **Terraform 1.6+**
- **AWS provider 5.x**
- Module pattern — `modules/` reusable, `environments/` composition
- State locking: DynamoDB
- Resource naming: `leanmgmt-<env>-<service>-<detail>`
- Common tags: Environment, Project, ManagedBy=terraform, Owner
- Least-privilege IAM — wildcard resource yasak
- GitHub OIDC — long-lived AWS keys yok
- KMS customer-managed keys (CMK) — DB, S3, Secrets için

### Avoid

- AWS console'dan manuel resource (Terraform yönetsin)
- `*` IAM resource
- `0.0.0.0/0` Security Group ingress (ALB dışında)
- `skip_final_snapshot = true` prod DB'de
- Plaintext secret Terraform'da (initial value console)
- Cross-environment dependency (dev bağımsız çalışsın)

## Done Definition

- [ ] `terraform init` dev/staging/prod için hatasız
- [ ] `terraform plan` dev — 0 değişiklik (idempotent)
- [ ] `terraform apply` dev — başarıyla çalışıyor
- [ ] Dev Aurora cluster reachable (ECS task'tan)
- [ ] Dev Redis reachable
- [ ] Dev S3 documents bucket encryption enabled (SSE-KMS)
- [ ] Dev Secrets Manager 5 secret (JWT current, JWT previous, refresh current, refresh previous, encryption) — initial değer console'dan set
- [ ] Dev ALB public, HTTPS only (ACM cert), HTTP→HTTPS redirect
- [ ] Dev CloudFront dağıtımı ALB önünde
- [ ] Dev WAF rule set (AWS managed rules)
- [ ] GitHub Actions OIDC role provision edilmiş
- [ ] Terraform state S3 bucket versioning + encryption + MFA delete (prod)
- [ ] Basic CloudWatch alarms (API 5xx rate, DB CPU)
- [ ] Staging + prod TF çalışıyor ama manuel apply (güvenlik)
- [ ] Commit: `feat(infra): complete AWS infrastructure via terraform for 3 environments`

## Explicit Don'ts

- Application code (sadece infra)
- Production DB data load (empty)
- Custom domain DNS (manual setup veya Faz 9)
- Full CI/CD pipeline (Faz 9)
- Advanced monitoring stack (Faz 9)
- EKS (ECS Fargate — simpler, adequate)

## Related ADRs

- ADR-0003: AWS eu-central-1 region (data residency)
- ADR-0004: Aurora PostgreSQL over RDS standard (serverless v2 option)
- ADR-0005: ECS Fargate over EKS (operational simplicity)
- ADR-0006: 3-account isolation (security boundary)
- ADR-0007: GitHub OIDC vs IAM keys (zero long-lived credentials)

